{"tid":926968,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國情報主管：華為構成安全威脅","createTime":"2018-12-03T23:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T02:41:32.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8bf12b3ab1f81f949dda534959ec1c9b428369","tid":926968,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:52:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">英國情報主管：華為構成安全威脅</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001080509?full=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001080509%3Ffull%3Dy&d=rSuNKG3kIeh9F4kELdDWWleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=c005e3ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001080509?full=y</a><br />\n<br />\n英國秘密情報局（SIS，通稱「軍情六處」，即MI6）局長亞歷克斯&bull;揚格(Alex Younger)在難得的一次演講中表達了針對中國電信設備製造商華為(Huawei)的安全擔憂，突顯北京方面在新興技術領域日益增強的主導地位對英國及其盟友構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n揚格此番演講的聽眾是蘇格蘭聖安德魯斯大學(University of St Andrews)的學生，30年前他曾在該校就讀。揚格表示，在美國、紐西蘭及澳大利亞等密切情報夥伴禁止華為參與未來5G移動網路的建設後，英國不得不對華為做出「一些決定」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">揚格說：「我們需要決定，在我們的一些盟友已經採取非常明確的立場後，我們需要在多大程度上接受中國對這些技術和平台的所有權。」<br />\n</span></span><br />\n在美國加緊施壓後，英國和德國對華為越發警惕。目前英國使用的一些華為設備被嵌入英國電信網路的核心，這些設備受到一個專門實驗室的測試，該實驗室由隸屬於數字情報機構&mdash;&mdash;政府通信總部(GCHQ)的國家網路安全中心(NCSC)的情報負責人監督。<br />\n<br />\n然而<span style=\"color: red;\">揚格表示，5G時代的到來將加大對華為設備監控的難度，中國的「法律和道德框架」、以及全球實力、政治及資金向亞洲的快速轉移，使這一威脅更具挑戰性。<br />\n<br />\n「中國有著不同的法律和道德框架。」揚格補充道。「他們可以在我們只能夢想的規模上使用並操縱數據集。」<br />\n</span><br />\n揚格表示，中國、俄羅斯和朝鮮等敵對國家發動的網路攻擊構成日益嚴重的威脅，這一點正在改變軍情六處基於老派人類諜報技術的運作方式。他說：「我們正將注意力轉移到人類與技術的連接點上。」"},{"pid":"36a6e6851f45795eadfbb4216bf73839b33bcfce","tid":926968,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:55:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">侵侵又贏</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec1cf66eed90115536267c3f47954ffe40295c3","tid":926968,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2118b9a6756283dc2f0fd8447deeec9f36106be3","tid":926968,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:34:19.000Z","msg":"五眼聯盟<br />\n<br />\n基本上都表左態<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4adda478874e42734e3501b611d40499558fb5","tid":926968,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"跟大隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0c787b9ac07a2c7cab820e717161727a5f14ea","tid":926968,"uid":18127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:40:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72f189237ab43b8445118499a686d8d3709be05e","tid":926968,"uid":37739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:54:23.000Z","msg":"又嬴"},{"pid":"025b6ab8e64bd016dc131fd3282bcd3f8c96a40e","tid":926968,"uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"de0c787b9ac07a2c7cab820e717161727a5f14ea","tid":926968,"uid":18127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:40:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"支那人繼續愚昧就啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好咁快畀佢地醒<br />\n等佢地犯更大嘅錯，得罪更多人先<br />\n之後一鋪清袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43639451657b2efeb5d1e8b27d999d2409a8c2f9","tid":926968,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:02:13.000Z","msg":"你唔好死撚咗先話自己有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p